# Vercel Deployment Configuration for Next.js

# 1. Push your code to a GitHub, GitLab, or Bitbucket repository.
# 2. Go to https://vercel.com/import and import your repository.
# 3. Vercel will auto-detect Next.js and set up the build for you.
# 4. If you need custom environment variables, add them in the Vercel dashboard after import.
# 5. After deploy, acesse: https://<your-vercel-url>/adm

